::Feline::

She smiled," Never had a half dead bot make a pass at me before." She 
said with a slight chuckle. She soldered some more wires and put the 
small metal plates on his head.  She had almost completed the head 
reapairs.  SHe went to her work bench and got the chip.  She 
installed it at the base of his brain case.  She smiled and finished 
the head repairs.  She then started back on the neck and worked on 
down.  She looked up at K-9,"This is going to take a while, he is 
badly damaged.  You can go to the mess hall and get somethingif you 
like? Or stay here and get bored." she said with a smile and a slight 
chuckle, "Most bots think repair work is boring, unless your the one 
getting repaired."
